data.description: Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to own your private 11+ Acre oasis! This 3000+ sqft gated home boasts 4 bedrooms, a bonus room, and 2.5 bathrooms. Recent upgrades include new hardwood floors in the entry, living, and dining areas, an updated, spacious kitchen with new tile floors, kitchen cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a water filtration system. Both the half bath downstairs and the full bath upstairs have been renovated. The primary suite features an updated private bath and custom walk-in closet. Enjoy the large covered deck, perfect for entertaining, and a spa. Priced competitively, with a 1yr home warranty plus closing cost contribution from our Preferred Lender. Don't let this opportunity slip away!
